hopobject.body: We were at school together fertile seed reviews Once Harry Styles started inking his body, there was no stopping the One Direction star. The singer's most recent work of body art comes in the form of a large butterfly tattoo smack in the center of his ribcage. Styles' tattoo artist Liam Sparkes posted this headless shot on Flickr in January 2013, and a rep for the teen heartthrob has now confirmed to E! News that it is indeed a photo of Harry's new tat. Check out more of the singer's massive amount of body ink ...
